Victoria Mallory https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria_Mallory 0 Victoria Mallory (September 20, 1948 – August 30, 2014) was an American singer and actress, best known for originating the role of Anne Egerman in the Broadway musical A Little Night Music.
